com.sayem.appium.pagefactory.framework.browser.mobile

Class IOSMobileBrowser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sayem.appium.pagefactory.framework.browser.Browser<io.appium.java_client.AppiumDriver>
      • com.sayem.appium.pagefactory.framework.browser.mobile.MobileBrowser
        • com.sayem.appium.pagefactory.framework.browser.mobile.IOSMobileBrowser

  • public class IOSMobileBrowser
extends MobileBrowser
    Known bug of Apple from Xcode 5 and iOS 7.1 Simulator - swipe is not working on simulator. As a workaround, using scrollTo in JavaScript. As in real devices regular swipe works but not scrollTo, using the regular command as well
